'''南洋藝術學院'''（簡稱：'''南藝'''；{{lang-en|''' Nanyang Academy of Fine Arts'''}}，縮寫：'''NAFA'''；{{lang-ms|Akademi Seni Halus Nanyang}}）是[[新加坡|新加坡]]歷史最悠久的第三級藝術教育機構，創始人是藝術家[[林學大|林學大]]。

二戰期間一度關閉。1946年，隨著[[日本投降|日本投降]]，林學大在另外兩名董事會成員的支持下重開大學。<ref>{{cite book|last=Mahamood|first=Muliyadi|title=Modern Malaysian Art: from the pioneering era to the pluralist era (1930s-1990s)|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qoWl0Gl0pUkC&lpg=PA27&ots=RH6RiEGaHN&dq=%22Nanyang%20Academy%20of%20Fine%20Arts%22&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q=%22Nanyang%20Academy%20of%20Fine%20Arts%22&f=false|year=2007|publisher=Utusan Publications|access-date=2013-10-17|archive-date=2013-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025073939/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qoWl0Gl0pUkC&lpg=PA27&ots=RH6RiEGaHN&dq=%22Nanyang%20Academy%20of%20Fine%20Arts%22&pg=PA27#v=onepage&q=%22Nanyang%20Academy%20of%20Fine%20Arts%22&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

